      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark problems at Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has been verified against standard benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow. Published verification documentation confirms correct numerical implementation of the Navier-Stokes equations."
