      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values were compared against experimental measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. Maximum deviation was 11.4%, with mean absolute error of 7.2%, satisfying the Gradation 2 output comparison requirement."
