    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable as not-assessed at Gradation 1 per the MRL 2 assessment plan. CFD predictions of the normalized hemolysis index agree with experimental data within 11.4% across all operating points, and the relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1 for all worst-case conditions evaluated. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended use decision for this Class II CPB device.",
